flowchart LR
    A[Raw SSE chunks] --> B[SSEJsonBuffer.addChunk]
    B --> C{Complete event?}
    C -->|Yes| D[Split by double newline]
    D --> E[Extract data: lines]
    E --> F{Valid JSON?}
    F -->|Yes| G[jsonObjects array]
    F -->|No| H[tryExtractJson fallback]
    H --> G
    C -->|No| I[Buffer for next chunk]
